  "body": "Looking at the peering logs on Besu I saw that we received disconnect reasons from other peers with rlp list format but also without a list (just a byte).is it normal to not have the same format each time a peer disconnect?\r\n\r\nBesu is waiting for a list so we can't parse all of the reason (sometimes it's failing) \r\n\r\nexample of reasons I logged \r\n```\r\ngetReason 0xc104\r\ngetReason 0xc103\r\ngetReason 0x04\r\ngetReason 0x04\r\ngetReason 0xc104\r\ngetReason 0xc110\r\ngetReason 0x10\r\ngetReason 0x10\r\ngetReason 0xc110\r\ngetReason 0xc103\r\ngetReason 0xc103\r\ngetReason 0xc104\r\ngetReason 0xc110\r\ngetReason 0x10\r\ngetReason 0xc180\r\ngetReason 0x10\r\ngetReason 0x10\r\ngetReason 0xc110\r\ngetReason 0xc105\r\ngetReason 0xc110\r\n```",
